{"tid":1858764,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"哥狗根本係温室小花","createTime":"2020-02-03T01:53:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-03T06:14:40.000Z","uid":119094,"like":35,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"4ae1f046bd2db8415fa1870074eecb99870174de","tid":1858764,"uid":119094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T01:53:53.000Z","msg":"永遠教豪門 <br />\n仲要本身已經攞到盃<br />\n用返人地條龍骨咪當自自己功勞<br />\n<br />\n無限金錢 <br />\n金手指咁買人<br />\n買完唔啱就雪<br />\n下季又黎過<br />\n試問有邊個領隊可以咁<br />\n如果猁買咗隻耶狗咪要死攬住<br />\n邊有得想換就換<br />\n<br />\n個board 同金主<br />\n球隊上下都冇不和<br />\n冇普巴依d大佬<br />\n基本上都係聽哥狗order <br />\n<br />\n哥狗amateur mode都玩到隊波就死咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0253d3c93592f2f1d672c9cbfb18e805fa423869","tid":1858764,"uid":84081,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T02:25:49.000Z","msg":"清 識波<br />\n<br />\n拜仁拎住全盛時期既梅拿、利雲、刀疤、洛賓<br />\n都可以畀巴塞、皇馬大炒<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n巴塞冇哥狗照樣靠MSN拎歐聯<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n條撚屌根本冇料 唔識教防守 <br />\n下下靜係識買大明星後防要佢地自動波<br />\n<br />\n買簡些路返黎唔出 <br />\n情願出安祖連奴搞到輸畀曼<br />\n迷戀Mendy搞到輸畀狼<br />\n巴禾次次出黎都失波 完全冇訓練好<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f1d0b7eaf5f85b2d2beb90ce15a2a7389c9a2ae","tid":1858764,"uid":43557,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T02:30:31.000Z","msg":"之前笑鳩哥狗廢俾班鏝迷屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n班傻仔以為哥狗真係咁撚勁"},{"pid":"a29f5060fe1d2f93a339d1c5bc41b969befbd4be","tid":1858764,"uid":119094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3f1d0b7eaf5f85b2d2beb90